gov.va.isaac.config

Class IsaacAppConfigWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.isaac.config.generated.IsaacAppConfig
      • gov.va.isaac.config.IsaacAppConfigWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsaacAppConfigI

    @Service
 @Singleton
public class IsaacAppConfigWrapper
extends IsaacAppConfig
implements IsaacAppConfigI
    IsaacAppConfigWrapper An ugly hack to make the generated (@link IsaacAppConfig} class implement the IsaacAppConfigI But it also gives us a place to set up some defaults, if the user provided data was unreadable / missing.
    Author:
    Dan Armbrust

      • getDefaultChangeSetUrl

        public String getDefaultChangeSetUrl()
        Description copied from interface: IsaacAppConfigI
        The default SVN or GIT URL that will be used to synchronize user profiles and changesets for this bundle. With SSH urls, such as "ssh://someuser@csfe.aceworkspace.net..." the contents between 'ssh://' and '@' should be replaced with the currently logged in user's syncUserName - as specified in that users profile before using this value. This may may differ from IsaacAppConfigI.getDefaultChangeSetUrl() if the user has changed the value.
        Specified by:
